description:
**OVERSIZED FIT**: Roomy, generous fit through the body.
**WATER-RESISTANT POLYESTER TAFFETA**:  Durable heavyweight quilted coat.  Fully lined, quilted and insulated. Designed to keep you warm even on the coldest winter days.
This product contains 100% Recycled Claim Standard (RCS) certified recycled polyester
**LONG PUFFER**: This long puffer jacket brings endless comfort and warmth, and is the perfect jacket for all your winter adventures. Layer with a sweater or fleece sweatshirt for the colder winter months.
**DETAILS**: Features an a-line shape, front zipper and snap closure, front pockets, elastic cuffs for comfort, and a hood with adjustable bungee cord and toggle. Side seam zippers at hem for versatile styling.
**Features a 2-Way Zipper**: To close, pull down the upper slider until it touches the bottom slider. Insert the separable pin to the very bottom of the bottom slider (incomplete insertion may cause issues). Pull up the upper slider with the left hand. To open, pull down the top slider until it touches the bottom slider. Pull out the separable pin with the right hand.
